maryContaineruniface_104tyx1665702670831.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tyx1665702670831.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tyx1665702670831.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tyx1665702670831\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies that the print destination will be restored to the default printer at the\n      end of a print job.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tyx1665702670831__topic_d145646e1_d145647e1_d145648e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tyx1665702670831__p_d145649e1_d145650e1_d145651e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DefaultPrinter</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"tyx1665702670831__section_w3246ab1b5b3_w3247ab1b5_w3248ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tyx1665702670831__table_d17753e1_d17754e1_d17755e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vas1665702670549.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vas1665702670549.html\" title=\"The [printer] section of the initialization file defines the fonts used for printing, and logical printer definitions.\">[printer]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tyx1665702670831__section_pxj_rgz_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777381e108\">Example</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"tyx1665702670831__pre_e